Package: rtai-modules-${kpkg:Kernel-Version}
Architecture: any
Provides: rtai-modules
Conflicts: rtai-modules
Replaces: rtai-modules
Description: RTAI modules for Linux (kernel ${kpkg:Kernel-Version})
 This package contains the set of loadable kernel modules for the RTAI realtime
 extension, the testsuite, the calibrate tool and other runtime programs
 depending on the kernel modules.
 .
 This package contains the compiled kernel modules for Linux ${kpkg:Kernel-Version}
 .
 To use the modules with your kernel, you need to patch the kernel and rebuild
 the kernel together with the modules. (I.e. you always need both, the patched
 kernel, _and_ the modules.) See the instructions in the rtai-source package.
